        <Parent_String>apartments [300004063], combinations of rooms [300075458], interior spaces (spaces by location) [300078790], rooms and spaces by location or context [300004011], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
